title: Apple Aced It! (…almost)
description:
Another year, another WWDC (without an invite). I'm not bitter though. Speaking of bitter, do you taste a 13" MacBook Pro with a Touch Bar in your mouth too? We got a new M2 MacBook Air (other, stupid hardware as well), iOS 16, macOS 13 Ventura, iPadOS 16, and so many other crazy awesome new features!
